overview:
Pricemap offers the internet users the possibility to search and compare prices on products and services from companies all over the world and also grants the companies the opportunity to advertise free their products and services on the website.

PricemapWeb.com is available internationaly and is based on the idea of a free global market where the buyer and the seller can easily find out any information regarding the offers, the alternatives and the prices in order to optimise their buget.

The website has a search option where users can chose the desired product types from a list of categories , they then can select the option to view results from entire World or just from certain cities and finally they can group the results by Items/Product Type/Service in order to find the best price for that certain item or to group by City in which case they can get overviews of different cities.

By registering for free their products/services on PriceMap company owners obtain free advertising.
